---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Beloved John Dev"
  description="Privacy policy for Beloved John Dev website and services."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <Navbar slot="navbar" />
  
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>

      <p>
        At <strong>Beloved John Dev</strong>, your privacy is respected.
        This website is a simple informational website intended to describe web development services.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Collection</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not collect personal information directly.
        There are no forms, user accounts, or databases on this website.
      </p>

      <h2>Contacting Me</h2>
      <p>
        If you choose to contact me via email, WhatsApp, or Telegram,
        your information is used only to respond to your inquiry and discuss your project.
        I do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies & Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        This website may use basic analytics tools in the future to understand general website traffic
        (such as page visits and device types).
        These tools do not collect personally identifiable information.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        This website contains links to third-party services such as WhatsApp and Telegram.
        These services have their own privacy policies, and I am not responsible for their practices.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This website is not intended for children under the age of 13,
        and no personal information is knowingly collected from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated occasionally.
        Any changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy,
        you can contact me via the methods listed on this website.
      </p>

      <p class="back-link">
        <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
  
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-page p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .back-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .back-link a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
